    <item>
      <title>嘉信理财的琼斯谈债券收益率、市场和选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/schwab-s-jones-on-bond-yields-markets-election-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉信理财首席固定收益策略师 Kathy Jones 表示，通胀正在朝着正确的方向发展，她预计本周的 CPI 报告将较为疲软。她还谈到了企业债务的环境，并表示债券市场并不关心总统选举。她正在接受“彭博收盘”节目的采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/schwab-s-jones-on-bond-yields-markets-election-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:37:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>零售助力衍生品ETF繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/etfs-gaining-popularity-via-influencers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 TikTok、YouTube 和 Reddit 等平台上，金融界的网红们正在推广一种新的股市投机方式——宣称乍一看，收益可以达到 100% 甚至更高。彭博社的 Denitsa Tsekova 与 Katie Greifeld 一起在“彭博市场”节目中讨论。
（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/etfs-gaining-popularity-via-influencers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:34:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starboard 斥资 10 亿美元入股辉瑞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-takes-1b-stake-in-pfizer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，激进投资者 Starboard Value 已入股辉瑞公司约 10 亿美元，并试图推动这家陷入困境的制药巨头扭亏为盈。彭博社的 Liana Baker 与 Katie Greifeld 一起在“彭博市场”节目中讨论这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-takes-1b-stake-in-pfizer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行前官员预计十月份将大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/former-bank-of-canada-official-sees-jumbo-rate-cut-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行管理机构的一位前成员表示，官员应该在本月晚些时候将借贷成本降低半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/former-bank-of-canada-official-sees-jumbo-rate-cut-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于循环信贷下降，美国消费者借贷增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-consumer-borrowing-growth-slows-on-drop-in-revolving-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份，美国消费者借贷增长速度低于一个月前，受到信用卡余额 2021 年 3 月以来最大降幅的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-consumer-borrowing-growth-slows-on-drop-in-revolving-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:05:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Elliott 收购 Citgo 为委内瑞拉投资者带来罕见胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-s-citgo-bid-sets-up-venezuela-investors-for-rare-payoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉国有石油公司过去五年没有向债券持有人支付一分钱。然而，持有某只特定证券的投资者正准备获得巨额回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-s-citgo-bid-sets-up-venezuela-investors-for-rare-payoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 14:13:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行警告亚马逊云计算业务“实力不足” 股价遭下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 股价周一下跌，此前分析师罕见下调其评级，理由是担心明年的利润率趋势，而云计算业务的增长不太可能弥补这一影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-cut-as-wells-fargo-warns-cloud-strength-not-enough</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
